snippet.title: Intellivision - Tower of Doom © 1986 INTV - Gameplay
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Monsters. Magic. Good. Evil. Strength. Cunning. Traps. Mazes. You are about to face the greatest challenge any mortal has ever known -- the Tower of Doom. Explore winding corridors! Collect magical treasures! Battle vile monsters! Escape perilous traps!
